N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 45.10 - Confidentiality

State Regulations

Medical, financial and personal information provided to the Adult Cystic Fibrosis Assistance Program to establish and maintain eligibility shall be kept confidential in accordance with Public Health Law, section 206.1(j). Notes
